    },
    "description": {
      "zh": "Izhmash机械厂开发的SV-98升级型号，采用可调节铝制骨架式枪托。该厂期望升级版能降低生产成本，同时提升维护便利性与射击精度。2017年卡拉什尼科夫集团接管了SV-98的生产线。",
      "en": "An upgraded SV-98 variant developed by Izhmash featuring an adjustable aluminum skeleton type stock. Izhmash expected the upgraded variant to be more economical to produce and offer improved maintainability and accuracy of fire. In 2017 Kalashnikov Concern took over production of the SV-98."
